0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-heaton">保罗·希顿 (Paul Heaton)</a>宣布与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lightning-seeds">Lightning Seeds</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a>在谢菲尔德举办一场大型演出 - 请在下面查看所有详细信息。</p><p>这位创作型歌手兼前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-housemartins">Housemartins</a>主唱将于 2025 年 5 月 25 日星期日在该市的布拉莫尔巷体育场（他心爱的谢菲尔德联队的主场）登顶，这是他迄今为止最大的个人头条演出之一。</p><p>希顿将与他的现场乐队和特邀歌手 Rianne Downey 一起在舞台上表演。 Lightning Seeds 和 Shed Seven 将提供支持。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，即将举行的音乐会对希顿来说具有“巨大的个人意义”——他从小就支持谢菲尔德联队，并且在童年时期也住在这座钢铁城。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800308" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800308" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800308" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven.jpg" alt="保罗·希顿 (Paul Heaton) 在谢菲尔德布拉莫巷 (Bramall Lane) 演出海报" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-Lightning-Seeds-Shed-Seven-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/1